data.oai_dc:dc: GENEPOP file of SNP genotypes for 191 white-footed mice

GENEPOP file of SNP genotypes for 191 white-footed mice generated using ddRAD-Seq. SNPs and GENEPOP file were generated using Stacks version 1.21. Sequences were not reference-aligned, so SNPs appear in an arbitrary order. File is compressed in a ZIP archive for ease of downloading.
